---

---

<section id="about" class="py-24 bg-gray-900 border-b border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Ambient glow -->
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-green-900/5 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <!-- Header -->
            <div class="mb-16">
                <p class="text-xs font-mono text-green-400 tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Sobre mí</p>
                <p class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white leading-tight max-w-2xl">
                    Diseño y construyo soluciones digitales pensadas para <span class="text-green-400">funcionar en negocios reales</span>, no solo para verse bien.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Two-column layout -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-20">
                <!-- Left: Paragraphs -->
                <div class="space-y-5 text-base text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed">
                    <p>
                        Mi enfoque combina desarrollo web, automatización, soporte técnico e inteligencia artificial aplicada. Me gusta entender primero el problema del negocio y después construir una solución simple, clara y mantenible.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Trabajo especialmente con negocios locales que necesitan una presencia online profesional, captar más clientes, ordenar sus procesos o dejar de depender de tareas manuales repetitivas.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-green-400/80 font-medium">
                        No busco complicar los proyectos con tecnología innecesaria. Busco que la solución sea útil, fácil de mantener y adaptada al momento real del negocio.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Right: Principles cards -->
                <div>
                    <p class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 tracking-widest uppercase mb-5">Mi forma de trabajar</p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:bg-green-500/20 transition-colors">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Claridad antes que complejidad</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:bg-green-500/20 transition-colors">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Tecnología cuando aporta valor</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:bg-green-500/20 transition-colors">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
                                    <circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"></circle>
                                    <polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"></polyline>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Diseño limpio y funcional</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:bg-green-500/20 transition-colors">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Soluciones preparadas para mantenerse</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.03] border border-white/[0.06] hover:bg-white/[0.05] hover:border-white/10 transition-all duration-300 group">
                            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:bg-green-500/20 transition-colors">
                                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-300 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Comunicación directa y alcance bien definido</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
